\n GET.summary: Get Root Cause Analysis Results List
\n GET.description: Returns a list of the latest root cause analysis results for a specified check.

parameters.name: limit
parameters.description: Limits the number of returned results to the specified quantity.

parameters.name: from
parameters.description: Return only results with timestamp of first test greater or equal to this value. Format is UNIX timestamp.

parameters.name: to
parameters.description: Return only results with timestamp of first test less or equal to this value. Format is UNIX timestamp.
